data.description: Welcome Home to Your Beautiful New Home in Global Manor! Great Price $322,900!  House is Better than New with many Upgrades throughout this Gorgeous House!  Owner's Attention to Details Inside and Out will make this the Perfect Pace to call Home!  Open Floor Plan provides the ideal setting to enjoy Holiday Celebrations with Family & Friends!  Spacious Great Room is Open to Kitchen & Dining Area. Upgraded Plank Flooring is installed in the Living Room, Kitchen/Dining and Hallway.   White Cabinets, Granite Counter Tops & Pantry provide Extra Storage and Work Space.  Stainless Stove, Microwave, Refrigerator and Dishwasher are included. This Single Level Home has 3 Bedrooms, 2 Full Bathrooms & an Office/Flex Space. Separate Laundry Room with Shelves. New Front Door & Light Fixtures 2 Car Garage. Extra Wide Concrete Driveway. Private Patio with View of Land & Mature Trees in Back. Very convenient location with easy access to Murfreesboro, Shelbyville, Schools & Shopping.100% USDA Financing.
